*.swp
*~

# The engine is built inside a Chromium checkout (see build.sh) — no build
# outputs live in this repo. Nothing to ignore there.
#
# Tracked on purpose: src/ (the host), patches/ (applied to the donor tree),
# docs/ (specs + demo PNGs), README.md, build.sh, PROGRESS.md.
#
# vendor/reference/ holds copied upstream Blink files used only as a reading
# reference while developing the host. Keep it out of the repo (it's a verbatim
# copy of Chromium source, not our code):
vendor/reference/

# build output of scripts/build-lib.sh (libminiblink2 SDK)
dist/
